Class: ExportOptionsFlash

ExportOptionsFlash

new ExportOptionsFlash()

Options for exporting a document as a Macromedia® Flash® (SWF) file, used with the exportFile method. All properties are optional. When you export a document, the appropriate file extension is appended automatically. You should not include any file extension in the file specification.
Source:
